1. Data Binding  -  Sharing data inside a component

  i. One Way Binding
      html -> ts  OR ts-> html
      ts - component
      html - view

      a. Component -> View [ts -> html]

          string interpolation - {{expression}}
          property binding - [attribute] = "property"

      b. View -> Component [html -> ts]

          Event binding - (event name) = "function name()"
          Event binding using ($event) - (event name)= "function name()"

  ii. Two Way Binding

2. Angular Routing - to set a path for a component
    {
        path:value, component: component class name
    }


3. Angular directives - to manipulate DOM elements

3. Component directives

4. Structural directives
    a. ngFor

5. Angular Forms:-

    a. Template driven Forms( first html design) - used for html page designing
    b. Model driven forms( first ts file -> html design) - used for advanced  validation methods
        i. Reactive Forms Module - [form group,array,control]
            we can directly add vallidation methods
            Add validation
            import Reactive forms modules

6. Local Storage
    setItem
    getItem
    removeItem

7. Parent Child Communication
    Parent to child communication  -  @Input()
    Child to parent communication  -  @Output()

8. Angular Pipes
    {{value-expression | date [:format [timezone]]}}

9. Frontend and Backend Integration
    Import HTTPClientModule  -  for creating HTTP Request
    Inject HTTPClient
    Using HTTPClientModule  -  for using API 

10. Asynchronous call
        RxJs - Reactive Extension for JavaScript
            =>To solve asynchronous request events
    i. Observable (Alternate of Promise)
        a. Resolve - subscribe()
        b. Reject - catch()